{
  "page": "Quaro",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Quaro</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\nKhal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>'s <i>khalasar</i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n~ <a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Quaro</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> warrior assigned to the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khas\" title=\"Khas\">khas</a></i> of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> within the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> of Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quaro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Quaro wears bells in his hair.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He has dark, almond-shaped eyes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quaro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quaro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Quaro is one of four young warriors assigned to guard <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>. When <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> attacks his sister in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a>, Quaro advises Daenerys to take an ear from Viserys to teach him respect.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> He later accompanies Daenerys during her visit to the Western Market in <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a>, challenging <a href=\"/index.php/Rakharo\" title=\"Rakharo\">Rakharo</a> to a friendly eating contest. Quaro helps stop an assassination attempt on Daenerys's life by a wineseller.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the raid on the <a href=\"/index.php/Lhazareen\" title=\"Lhazareen\">Lhazareen</a> settlement, Quaro is commanded by Daenerys to stop the Dothraki riders raping the captured <a href=\"/index.php/Eroeh\" title=\"Eroeh\">Eroeh</a>. Though he initially protests against stopping it, he complies with her command.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Daenerys intends to have Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a> healed by <a href=\"/index.php/Mirri_Maz_Duur\" title=\"Mirri Maz Duur\">Mirri Maz Duur</a> using blood magic, Drogo's <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodrider\" title=\"Bloodrider\">bloodriders</a> try to stop it from happening. In the ensuing fight, Quaro is killed by <a href=\"/index.php/Qotho\" title=\"Qotho\">Qotho</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quaro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Quaro is remembered by Daenerys when she thinks back to the followers who have died under her service.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Quaro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_61\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 61\">Chapter 61</a>, Daenerys VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_54\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 54\">Chapter 54</a>, Daenerys VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><